WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.145 --> 00:00:10.145
Freight forwarding is a fast moving industry.

00:00:10.522 --> 00:00:13.282
Advances in technology have made the business

00:00:13.833 --> 00:00:15.713
almost unrecogniseable

00:00:15.913 --> 00:00:17.393
from even a few short years ago.

00:00:18.373 --> 00:00:21.373
However, one key quality remains

00:00:21.787 --> 00:00:23.787
It is the individual with knowledge

00:00:23.887 --> 00:00:26.787
that moves forward and succeeds.

00:00:29.737 --> 00:00:31.737
For the first time in Ireland

00:00:31.856 --> 00:00:33.456
this knowledge is now attainable

00:00:33.933 --> 00:00:35.933
through a professional qualification

00:00:36.157 --> 00:00:38.157
that is recognised worldwide

00:00:38.878 --> 00:00:40.878
can be completed within 1 year

00:00:41.822 --> 00:00:46.862
and is proven to enhance the career prospects of its graduates

00:00:47.691 --> 00:00:49.691
From the end of this month

00:00:49.946 --> 00:00:51.946
the Irish International Freight Association

00:00:51.965 --> 00:00:54.965
is offering those with higher career aspirations

00:00:55.036 --> 00:00:56.035
the opportunity

00:00:56.121 --> 00:00:59.137
to study for the FIATA Diploma in Freight Forwarding 

00:01:00.759 --> 00:01:02.759
This course of study was initiated

00:01:03.211 --> 00:01:06.211
in 1996 by FIATA in Zurich Switzerland

00:01:06.286 --> 00:01:08.286
and since then more than 5,000

00:01:08.724 --> 00:01:11.724
freight forwarding and supply chain management professionals 

00:01:12.488 --> 00:01:14.488
have been awarded the diploma.

00:01:14.907 --> 00:01:16.907
The benefits of the course are...

00:01:17.989 --> 00:01:19.989
It's use of Blended Learning means

00:01:20.631 --> 00:01:22.631
you continue in fulltime employment

00:01:23.226 --> 00:01:25.226
while studying in your own time

00:01:25.870 --> 00:01:27.870
and at your own pace

00:01:28.281 --> 00:01:30.281
You also attend class tutorials delivered by

00:01:30.969 --> 00:01:32.969
experienced freight forwarding professionals

00:01:33.241 --> 00:01:37.241
and you complete the course in less than 10 months. 

00:01:40.980 --> 00:01:42.980
This is an excellent opportunity for you

00:01:43.846 --> 00:01:45.846
to gain an official qualification in your

00:01:46.405 --> 00:01:48.405
own profession and will further your career.

00:01:49.391 --> 00:01:56.390
For full details please see our web site at www.iifa.ie

